product.title: Mocha & Tofu Bears Seagull Friend Unisex Hoodie
product.body_html:
• Description
  • FAQ
  • Shipping

  • Feel the seabreeze and the joy

    You'll love this Mocha & Tofu Bears Seagull Friend Unisex Hoodie! It's perfect for any ocean lover or sunny day fan. Whether you're sailing, surfing, or just chilling, this hoodie will keep you cozy and stylish. Plus, it features a cute seagull friend that will make you smile. Don't miss this awesome hoodie!

    This kawaii hoodie is available in seven different sizes for all to wear, measurements are shown below. It is best to measure your chest and length, and then choose a size according to the result to simplify the various international measurement.

    Size (inches) XS S M L XL XXL XXXL
    Bust 34 37 38 40 41 44 44
    Length 25 26 27 28 29 30 31
    Sleeve 21 22 23 23 24 25 26
                   
    Size (cm) XS S M L XL XXL XL
    Bust 88 94 98 102 106 110 114
    Length 64 66 69 72 75 78 80
    Sleeve 53 56 59 60 62 64 66


    Features

    🥰 Made from 100% premium polyester microfiber 
    😍 Promotes warmth, comfort, and durability

    All sizes:

    Measurements may be off by 1-5cm for rounding up to a whole number.                                                                                                                                                    If you are interested in more items like this, please check out our website www.kawaiies.com.                 

  • Please follow the washing labels when cleaning the garment:

     Max temperature 30c, or cold water. Reverse garment to protect the print.

     Do not bleach

     Dry by the sun or hang it to dry. 

     Dry cleaning

     

  • FREE Tracked Shipping to the United States, Canada, United Kingdom, Australia, New Zealand, Germany, Spain, France, Italy, Austria, Netherlands, and many more. Find out more here: Shipping Policy.

    Packaging time: 1-3 Business days

    Shipping time: Est 5-30 Business days
